The paper deals with the problem of trajectory planning for UAVs in the presence of dynamic obstacles, which is a common problem in robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also uses point cloud processing and trajectory estimation, which are common techniques in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.AI). The paper also involves control systems (cs.SY) and optimization (cs.LG) for trajectory planning.
